OL,3,CGovernment bans asylum seekers from
OL,4,Ctaking taxis to medical appointments
OL,6,FAsylum seekers have been banned from
OL,7,Ftaking a taxi to medical appointments,
OL,8,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FThe government said the new rules will
OL,12,Frestrict taxi use for medical travel
OL,13,Fto exceptional, evidence-based cases
OL,14,Fsuch as physical disability, pregnancy
OL,15,For serious illness.
OL,17,FAny such journey would require Home
OL,18,FOffice approval. It is understood the
OL,19,Fpolicy change comes after a Home
OL,20,FOffice review of transport
OL,21,Farrangements for asylum seekers.
