OL,6,FAll service providers will be required
OL,7,Fto stop using taxis for medical
OL,8,Fjourneys from February.
OL,10,FMahmood said the government is working
OL,11,Fwith providers to introduce
OL,12,Falternatives, such as public
OL,13,Ftransport, in a bid to save taxpayer
OL,14,Fmoney.
OL,16,F"This government inherited
OL,17,FConservative contracts that are
OL,18,Fwasting billions of taxpayers' hard-
OL,19,Fearned cash," she said.
