OL,3,CGovernment bans asylum seekers from
OL,4,Ctaking taxis to medical appointments
OL,6,F"I am ending the unrestricted use of
OL,7,Ftaxis by asylum seekers for hospital
OL,8,Fappointments, authorising them only in
OL,9,Fthe most exceptional circumstances.
OL,11,F"I will continue to root out waste as
OL,12,Fwe close every single asylum hotel."
OL,14,FIt comes as new figures show the
OL,15,Fnumber of asylum seekers being housed
OL,16,Fin UK hotels has risen by 13% in three
OL,17,Fmonths.
