OL,6,FMeanwhile, net migration to the UK has
OL,7,Ffallen to its lowest level since 2021,
OL,8,Faccording to figures from the Office
OL,9,Ffor National Statistics (ONS).
OL,11,FEarlier this month, Mahmood set out a
OL,12,Fraft of measures to overhaul the
OL,13,Fasylum system, aimed at deterring
OL,14,Fillegal migration to the UK and making
OL,15,Fit easier to deport people.
