OL,6,FThe proposed changes include making
OL,7,Frefugee status temporary, subject to
OL,8,Freviews every 30 months, and sending
OL,9,Frefugees home if their country is
OL,10,Fdeemed safe.
OL,12,FThe wide-ranging reforms drew
OL,13,Fcriticism from Labour backbenchers.
OL,15,FMahmood told MPs it was the
OL,16,F"uncomfortable truth" that the UK's
OL,17,Fgenerous asylum offer, compared with
OL,18,Fother European countries, is drawing
OL,19,Fpeople to UK shores, and for British
OL,20,Ftaxpayers the system "feels out of
OL,21,Fcontrol and unfair".
